{"tid":152653,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Wexit？雲加：可留多久就留多久","createTime":"2017-03-12T03:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T04:02:28.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"481cb9f5c7d68fe7eec2391ce33a38fbf91e7d03","tid":152653,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2XywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b4e4df9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】在歐聯被大炒出局後，阿仙奴領隊雲加備受壓力，更有球迷抗議要求他離隊，不過在周六領軍殺入英足盃4強後，雲加坦言仍會長期留隊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然對手只是非聯賽球隊林肯城，但強陣並有主場之利的阿仙奴也要戰至上半場補時階段才開紀錄，幸最終仍大勝5:0。雲加（Arsene Wenger）坦言球隊經過近期慘淡的戰績後，有一點信心危機。<br />\n<br />\n雲加說：「不過在下半場，球員的自信回來了。外界都有很多意見，但不代表他們的說話都是對的。我們要在場上證明我們的價值。」同時，他又大讚林肯城甚有組織，而且目標十分清晰。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴球迷賽前高舉寫上&ldquo;Wexit&rdquo;標語，促請雲加下台。這名詞顯然是借用&ldquo;Brexit&rdquo;，即英國脫歐的縮寫。對於球迷的抗議，雲加淡然表示：「我在過去已證明了，我對這家球會百分百地付出，可以留隊多久，我就留多久。我只會專注工作，任其他人去評論我的表現。」"},{"pid":"0eda95fd36058397c4223f335f4e28744ada10dc","tid":152653,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a521181bb29968528164dc96cedc5dc0496cd2","tid":152653,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0108f926b6da0adfb2cb563ed254abe9be9e540f","tid":152653,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>永續雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nching sick ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5091f5c745ae0d232a18d14b70776b1098d7ca11","tid":152653,"uid":3204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:09:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=